# Build context for docker/Dockerfile (the static frontend image). Keep it to
# what `vite build` needs: src/, convex/ (committed _generated), index.html, the
# vite/ts/tailwind configs, package*.json. Everything else is excluded.

.git
.DS_Store

# Reinstalled / rebuilt inside the image
node_modules
dist
**/node_modules
**/dist

# Other workspaces & tooling not needed to build the frontend
bridge
mcp
local-openclaw
docs
deploy
backend
frontend
nanobanana-output
.convex
.idea
.vscode
.claude
.agents

# Secrets / env / runtime config (never bake)
secrets
config.local.json
*.local.json
*.env
.env
.env.*
public/config.json

# Diagnostics
openclaw-frame-captures
*.ndjson
*.log
